# CareerNest Testing Suite — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

### 1. Mock Data Seed Script
- [seed-test-data.ts](file:///c:/webdevprojects/internship_placement/prisma/seed-test-data.ts) — Creates 3 Students (with resumes + 128-dim mock embeddings) and 1 Recruiter. Outputs a JWT token for manual testing.

### 2. Matches Endpoint
- [matches.controller.ts](file:///c:/webdevprojects/internship_placement/src/controllers/matches.controller.ts) — `GET /jobs/:id/matches` returns top 5 candidates by cosine similarity (`1 - (<=>)`).
- [index.ts](file:///c:/webdevprojects/internship_placement/src/index.ts) — Added `cookie-parser` middleware + matches route.

