### Test Helpers
- [prisma-mock.ts](file:///c:/webdevprojects/internship_placement/tests/helpers/prisma-mock.ts) — Deep PrismaClient mock
- [factories.ts](file:///c:/webdevprojects/internship_placement/tests/helpers/factories.ts) — [makeUser()](file:///c:/webdevprojects/internship_placement/tests/helpers/factories.ts#12-24), [makeResume()](file:///c:/webdevprojects/internship_placement/tests/helpers/factories.ts#25-38), [makeJob()](file:///c:/webdevprojects/internship_placement/tests/helpers/factories.ts#39-53)
- [app.ts](file:///c:/webdevprojects/internship_placement/tests/helpers/app.ts) — Express app factory for supertest

---

## How to Run

```bash
# Run all tests once
npm test

# Watch mode (re-runs on save)
npm run test:watch

# With coverage report
npm run test:coverage

# Run seed script (populates DB for manual testing)
npm run seed
```

